{"tid":2439101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"圖癱瘓經濟 遏制軍政府  緬民號召長期罷工","createTime":"2021-03-09T04:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:05:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e3e77c714aae20e75ec64228bdd65062eebbf4","tid":2439101,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/SS4XFCQC5JB5NL5TXTPTTOSVXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FSS4XFCQC5JB5NL5TXTPTTOSVXU%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=2442623c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FSS4XFCQC5JB5NL5TXTPTTOSVXU%2F&h=87ff6247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/SS4XFCQC5JB5NL5TXTPTTOSVXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n圖癱瘓經濟 遏制軍政府 <br />\n緬民號召長期罷工<br />\n<br />\n緬甸最少18個工會昨發起大罷工，計劃長期和全面癱瘓經濟，以支持由公務員發起的不合作運動，向上月奪走民選政府權力的軍方施壓。各大城市同日繼續有民眾上街示威，與軍警爆發激烈衝突，據報至少再多三人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c5i-k4RgVz6a_baXpTbnLvYOdAA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PAWINRNLIRAPZN255LVCNL2KO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc5i-k4RgVz6a_baXpTbnLvYOdAA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPAWINRNLIRAPZN255LVCNL2KO4.jpg&h=3ec8238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光響應全國大罷工的民眾昨天上街，齊舉三指抗爭手勢。<br />\n<br />\n大罷工由建造業、農業和製造業等行業的工會聯合發起，它們在聲明表示「讓商業和經濟活動繼續將助長軍方，他們在壓制緬甸人民的力量」，因此「現在是時候以行動保衞我們的民主」。示威領袖貌桑哈亦乘着國際婦女節呼籲女性不要忽視自己的力量，勇於參與反軍政府的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OufjjfWUNbHJknPXp8BNuQPNb68=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TWMBROG6SZGAHIBSXKOHIYI6WQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOufjjfWUNbHJknPXp8BNuQPNb68%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTWMBROG6SZGAHIBSXKOHIYI6WQ.jpg&h=c6acb532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光防暴警察射催淚彈，示威者四散。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武裝組織保護示威者<br />\n<br />\n在商界配合下，緬甸的經濟活動幾乎陷於停頓，主要商場關門，工廠停工，最大城市仰光只有少數茶店仍然營業，示威活動繼而。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n軍方未敢怠慢這場大罷工，前一晚已派人進駐仰光最少六間醫院，似為向不願效忠的醫護施壓，並派員在各地部署、巡邏和搜查民居，最少拘捕了41人。國營媒體指安全部隊進駐。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動已維持逾一個月，令人憂慮失去工資的公務員難以堅持下去，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZQ4DhHQH5i_vzfNSnrDI2Qo8sh4=/802x362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZ4NAKXIWFAHNIYFW3Y3GFITH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZQ4DhHQH5i_vzfNSnrDI2Qo8sh4%3D%2F802x362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZ4NAKXIWFAHNIYFW3Y3GFITH4.jpg&h=99d22eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曼德勒科技大學前天已有警察進駐。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日星泰僑民捐款暗撐<br />\n<br />\n另外，國內有「緬甸工程師」和PiTia等組織籌款，日本、新加坡、泰國和其他西方國家僑民也踴躍捐輸，默默在背後支持罷工者。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍政府鎮壓示威者的行動至今已造成逾50人死，惹來國際社會關注。繼。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/《緬甸前線》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dXHBEzpGooefERQaUxjFc4mfgF8=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LEKQSPQJ5FAXVPJ5RHP6XUXFBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdXHBEzpGooefERQaUxjFc4mfgF8%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLEKQSPQJ5FAXVPJ5RHP6XUXFBM.jpg&h=eb8c33e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光有女示威者拉起塔曼袍防線，嘗試阻止軍警推進。"}]}